  "title": "Duke Kunshan University",
  "description": "Learn about Duke Kunshan University and explore highly selective, globally-oriented liberal arts programs. As a global leading university in China, DKU world-class faculty involving students in scholarship and experiential learning programs.",
  "language": "en-US",
